OL,3,CLetby inquiry told steps should be
OL,4,Ctaken to root out 'bad apples' in the
OL,5,CNHS
OL,7,FThe inquiry over the crimes of serial
OL,8,Fbaby killer Lucy Letby has heard from
OL,9,Fan expert who compared failings in her
OL,10,Fcase to those of the Manchester GP and
OL,11,Fmass murderer Harold Shipman.
OL,13,FThe hearing at Liverpool Town Hall has
OL,14,Fbeen told formal steps should be in
OL,15,Fplace to deal with suspected "bad
OL,16,Fapples" in the NHS, following the
OL,17,Fnurse's killing of seven children and
OL,18,Fthe attempted murder of seven others
OL,19,Fat the Countess of Chester Hospital.
OL,26,@wD@^OUxD@GO]
