OL,3,CLetby inquiry told steps should be
OL,4,Ctaken to root out 'bad apples' in the
OL,5,CNHS
OL,7,FShe said the danger of assuming that
OL,8,Fsuch bad apples do not exist was
OL,9,Fhighlighted by the Clothier Inquiry
OL,10,Finto Allitt's crimes which concluded
OL,11,F"the main lesson the Grantham disaster
OL,12,Fshould serve is to heighten awareness
OL,13,Fin all those caring for children of
OL,14,Fthe possibility of a malevolent
OL,15,Fintervention as a cause of unexplained
OL,16,Fclinical events".
OL,18,FCounsel to the inquiry Rachel Langdale
OL,19,FKC asked: "From your perspective, how
OL,20,Fcan that be achieved to heighten
OL,21,Fawareness?"
OL,26,@sD@AOUxD@PO]{D@KOU}D@KO]
