OL,3,CLetby inquiry told steps should be
OL,4,Ctaken to root out 'bad apples' in the
OL,5,CNHS
OL,7,F"We know from other areas like fraud
OL,8,For sexual abuse, unless you have got
OL,9,Fthe procedures in place it's very
OL,10,Fdifficult for organisations to deal
OL,11,Fwith them.
OL,13,F"If someone is suspected of fraud
OL,14,Fthere is a series of steps that the
OL,15,Forganisation knows to take. I'm not
OL,16,Fsure the same clarity is there in an
OL,17,Fevent where someone is suspected of
OL,18,Fmurder or attempted murder."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@\O]
