OL,3,CLetby inquiry told steps should be
OL,4,Ctaken to root out 'bad apples' in the
OL,5,CNHS
OL,7,FShe acknowledged it was "extremely
OL,8,Fdifficult" for someone to initially
OL,9,Fvoice concerns about possible
OL,10,Fmalevolent acts.
OL,12,FShe said: "They may be met with what's
OL,13,Fcalled the credibility gap which was
OL,14,Fidentified in the Shipman inquiry. And
OL,15,Fthey may struggle to be heard or to
OL,16,Faddress the concerns.
OL,26,@oD@YOUpD@JO]tD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
