OL,3,CLetby inquiry told steps should be
OL,4,Ctaken to root out 'bad apples' in the
OL,5,CNHS
OL,7,FLetby, 34, from Hereford, is serving
OL,8,F15 whole-life orders after she was
OL,9,Fconvicted at Manchester Crown Court of
OL,10,Fmurdering seven infants and attempting
OL,11,Fto murder seven others, with two
OL,12,Fattempts on one of her victims, at the
OL,13,FCountess of Chester Hospital's
OL,14,Fneonatal unit between June 2015 and
OL,15,FJune 2016.
OL,17,FThe inquiry is expected to sit until
OL,18,Fearly 2025, with findings published by
OL,19,Flate autumn of that year.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
